Banyan Token Has Launched 
We are excited to announce the launch of Banyan Token on Base chain with a total supply of 1 billion tokens:
* Contract Address: 0xcf3155bc7c6660ab2fec8fb3a43c49abcc9a3211
* 50% allocated to liquidity pool (already provided)
* Remaining 50% is locked as follows: 
   * 30% for ecosystem development (6-month lock, 24-month linear vesting)
   * 15% for team (12-month lock, 12-month linear vesting)
   * 5% for advisors (6-month linear vesting)
Project Milestones 
Our achievements in Web3 social space include:
* Integration with leading social protocols: Farcaster, X, and Lens Protocol
* Multi-chain support across Solana, Base, and Ethereum
* Over 1,000 Frame app installations in Farcaster ecosystem
* More than 500 daily active users on platform
Strategic Roadmap
1. Enhance trading experience
2. Expand social protocol ecosystem
3. Strengthen Banyan Token utility and value proposition
